      <h2>Equipments</h2>
      <h3>Compute Infrastructure</h3>
      <p>VUB-ETRO has dedicated GPUs at the desktop for interactive coding and testing; specifically: 14x RTX 3090, 7x RTX 2080 Ti, 2x GeForce GTX 1080 Ti, and 1x Lambda server 4x RTX 2080 Ti. VUB-ETRO also has a GPU cluster (Tier-3) providing on-demand computing with: 4x NVIDIA A100 Tensor Core GPU (40GB and 80GB) and 4x NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090. Moreover, VUB has its own Tier-2, which provides on-demand computing with twenty A100 nodes (15x40GB; 5x80GB), and 10x H200 (with VUB-ETRO having priority at 2 of them). Moreover, we can freely access the Flemish Tier-1 (VSC) after submitting a compute project). The next Tier-1 at VUB (Sofia), represents a 12M€ investment and has started since the fall of 2025.</p>

